Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Maison.de.章樫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗稱 妖館
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一次 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖館
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不必擔心 凜凜蝶小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我定會好好保護您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了 凜凜蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也允許我接您放學 我深感榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼稍後請去用餐...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要向禦狐神君表達我的謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超市抽獎中的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哐當一聲 中大獎了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野太可愛了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身女僕裝加上一臉得意的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪裝飾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也幫妳想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野 朝我這裡看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不放在休息廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都往這裡走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭了 渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得妳待人差距太大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也請雪小路小姐多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家應該都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜凜蝶他們也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究 究竟什麼狀況了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妖館的安全系統啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全系統？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人想要入侵妖館時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全系統就會啟動 形成結界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來竟然藏在盆栽裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是假死狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假死狀態？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假死狀態就是說之前一直在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不被人發現 進到了裏面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點雲裏霧裏的 難道是我的錯？抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是小千野的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了這裡還有幾個結界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個結界都有一扇門和一個安全據點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個浮在那邊 就說明它在正常運作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使不做那些事 只要門是緊閉著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就進不來 放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一打開了門怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只開了一扇門 結界都會被削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到早上 妖怪就會消失 安全系統也會解除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前我們就在這裡呆著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天早上之前就是食人節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生存遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此情況下 明早之前都要聽我的話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是和兔子先生的約定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全劇終
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你怎麼變成豆貍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過太突然嚇了一跳 才變身了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這些 歌留多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡 當然是別的結界裡咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能違背同兔子先生的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 是很危險的妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用語言來描述都非常可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管怎樣看來今晚就只能在這過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太悠閒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您晚飯還沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 這些東西哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前準備好放在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來長夜漫漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野薔薇 那邊有很多東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來今晚還有很多時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守在歌留多身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼守
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在別的結界吧 我到那個結界去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管這結界會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救歌留多 我要撬開這扇命運之門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 兔子是不會說謊的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這裡 你也可以為小歌歌做點什麼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這結界裏面形成了無限回路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其時間流動和外面的世界是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的一小時相當於外面的一天到兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某些地方 還很適合訓練的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方說這個走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板是扭曲的 在這裡培養平衡感是非常有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持訓練到早上的話 保證能提升你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“再也不讓你們說我是病弱男孩 let's training！” 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了小歌歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都很冷靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看上去是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你現在和平常沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到在這房間裏 能服侍凜凜蝶小姐到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就冷靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 冷靜下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門窗都不能開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在密閉的房間 到早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說青春期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 是個表達謝意的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 原來如此 哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜凜蝶小姐看來心情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:13.21,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的母親 地球這一行星從誕生以來 過了46億年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 貓月先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類作為盟主 統領著這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會和你們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈真好呢 一家團圓的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:24.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在統領的過程中 會發生一些奇妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我以為和團圓一詞都無緣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙之事一直持續發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話題變得有點沉重呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 算了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我扯上關係的話 可會引火上身的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類始終貫徹自己的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其他物種尋求共存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 他一直都這樣子 爸爸也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野薔薇 別 突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是第一次 要溫柔點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也來 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼進攻 我可是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然進攻這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了 我是冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下個玩花牌吧 花牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐來教妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼表達謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 果然這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 怎麼能打退堂鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜凜蝶小姐 您要不要去沐浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡？這種時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天早上都不能離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這麼做可以放鬆下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 有點道理 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦狐神君 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 那個... 真是麻煩你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是應盡之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 本來我也應同您一起入浴 為您擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但男女有別 不能照顧周到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗好澡之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這種東西哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到凜凜蝶小姐這種裝扮 如同進入夢境般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話就別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛 多想將這樣子保存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 要不要拍張照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能把它當做待機畫面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把它放大 掛在墻上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事是不被允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是一條狗 卻用凜凜蝶小姐用過的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還用同一浴缸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你別洗了就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好您就寢的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 還不睏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦狐神君 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 明天之前我會好好保護凜凜蝶小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要不要躺下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 也能放鬆下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 我就躺下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事的話 請隨時吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 你別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我了 想睡的話就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜凜蝶小姐也請別在意我 早點休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓...讓...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你受累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明...明...明...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還要上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這番話 我受之有愧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧 我是為了凜凜蝶小姐而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保護好凜凜蝶小姐的話 我的存在就毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…是凜凜蝶小姐的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對這樣的我 說出這番話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,272)}{\fad(550,150)}但\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,430)}{\fad(550,150)}正\N因\N為\N如\N此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,163)}{\fad(550,850)}我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,434)}{\fad(550,850)}也\N想\N回\N報\N他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快天亮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺很有效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然結界中就是不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 不會吧 你當真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不這麼說 渡貍肯定會擔心小歌歌的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 這個是門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎哪扇門被打開了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別來打擾我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 渡貍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不良少年哦 盡管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡貍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雙雙 小蝶蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雙雙 我還以為我們再也見不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事真是太好了 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目先生把我們帶過來的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪某個笨蛋 毀了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想想制伏妖怪要來的快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制伏？不危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒妳想的那麼危險 怎麼說呢 就是有點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 禦狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前確實說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Obariyon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別名 背負小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏於夜路 會依附到路人身上的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言只是依附著路人 並不會加害於人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不給我放開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜凜蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜凜蝶小姐 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我跟在您身旁 卻有如此失態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 你不是說這是非常可怕的妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那種東西碰到凜凜蝶小姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈還蠻有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽依舊會升起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 食人節活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次教妳禁忌遊戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用給她看你修行成果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜凜蝶小姐 回房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小人村千野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖館的女僕 超喜歡打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不是自我介紹 是要做下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:24:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}下回可是出浴後悶悶不樂的小凜凜蝶邀請御狐神先生的故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 妖狐x僕SS 茶與距離
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥一臉得意
